<paragraph id="B3127C89F59DE6EA95AED16B1D6BE09C" pageId="0" pageNumber="8176">
A common species of dry hills and desert slopes (
<bibRefCitation id="09F159CD14EF8F81E82336BCBD1D0465" author="Stevensen, DW" editor="Flora of North America Editorial Committee, eds." journalOrPublisher="New York and Oxford" pageId="0" pageNumber="8176" title="Flora of North America North of Mexico" year="1993">Stevensen 1993</bibRefCitation>
), we collected this species along mesa tops and desert scrub communities north of MDRS along Cow Dung Road (Fig. 34). This species was previously reported for the nearby San Rafael Swell (
<bibRefCitation id="692C455C03FD46AD6FCBCFEF9A039845" author="Harris, JG" journalOrPublisher="Great Basin Naturalist" pageId="0" pageNumber="8176" pagination="79 - 87" title="A vascular flora of the San Rafael Swell, Utah" volume="43" year="1983">Harris 1983</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
